OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a rather cloudy start it
OL,6,Fwill be a dry day with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells developing later in the
OL,8,Fmorning and a sunny afternoon will
OL,9,Ffollow, though cloud may persist over
OL,10,Fnortheastern coasts. Very warm, with
OL,11,Flight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry evening with some
OL,14,Fsunshine. Overnight staying dry and
OL,15,Fclear in the eastm while parts of the
OL,16,Fwest will turn cloudier.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FRemaining dry with variable
OL,19,Famounts of cloud and some bright or
OL,20,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
